<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pound3" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pound,</orth> vb. to shut up as in a pinfold: <cit><quote>'twere best p. you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 1, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>we'll break our walls, rather than they shall p. us up,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.4.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 4, 17</bibl></cit>. cf. <emph>Impound.</emph>
